nodes.text: 2005 Topps Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith
2005 Topps Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith is a trading card set released by Topps in April 2005 to coincide with the then-upcoming prequel trilogy film, Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith.

The former Collecting section of StarWars.com featured first looks at Artist Sketch Cards by Kilian Plunkett, Tom Hodges, Dan Parsons, Joe Corroney, Cat Staggs, Monte Moore, Grant Gould, Robin Pronovost, Chris Trevas, Otis Frampton, Justin Chung, David Rabbitte, Matt Busch, Sarah Wilkinson, and Jeff Chandler.
